reviewText: An excellent history of one of the Carolina's favorite bands.  I would highly recommend this to all Embers' fans.
Bill Benner's did a great job on this video. If you love the Embers (As most of us do in Eastern NC) You will really enjoy this video!
Product arrived promptly. Enjoyed reviewing history of a favorite band.
